OL,7,FA 21-year-old woman felt "petrified
OL,8,Fand "unsafe" while undergoing
OL,9,Ftreatment for an eating disorder on
OL,10,Fmental health units in south Wales.
OL,12,FGeorgia Taylor, from Brynna, near
OL,13,FPontyclun, said her physical and
OL,14,Fmental health deteriorated after she
OL,15,Fwas admitted to psychiatric wards in
OL,16,FLlantrisant and Bridgend.
