OL,7,FGeorgia said she developed heart
OL,8,Fproblems and lost so much weight as an
OL,9,Finpatient that she was eventually
OL,10,Frushed to a medical ward for
OL,11,Flifesaving treatment.
OL,13,FIt follows a report by mental health
OL,14,Fcharity, Mind Cymru, that raises
OL,15,Fconcerns around mental health
OL,16,Finpatient care and safety. It
OL,17,Fhighlights staff shortages are
OL,18,Fnegatively impacting patients.
