OL,7,FThe Welsh Government has said its
OL,8,Fcommitment to prioritising mental
OL,9,Fhealth is reflected in a #2 million
OL,10,Finvestment into improving the quality
OL,11,Fand safety of the service.
OL,13,FGeorgia began to struggle with an
OL,14,Feating disorder at the age of fourteen.
OL,16,F"A lot of my friends were going on
OL,17,Fdiets and it's very big on social
OL,18,Fmedia to lose weight and to fit into
OL,19,Fthe norm of looking beautiful and
OL,20,Fslim," she explained.
