OL,7,F"But I took it too far. I struggled
OL,8,Fwith my eating disorder for a number
OL,9,Fof years before it got very serious."
OL,11,FOnce she turned eighteen, Georgia had
OL,12,Fto be transferred from CAMHS (Child
OL,13,Fand Adolescent Mental Health Services)
OL,14,Fto Adult Services.
