OL,7,FDuring a wait for support that Georgia
OL,8,Fsaid lasted several months, she
OL,9,Frelapsed and was sectioned to a mental
OL,10,Fhealth unit at Royal Glamorgan
OL,11,FHospital. She was transferred to
OL,12,FPrincess of Wales Hospital two weeks
OL,13,Flater.
OL,15,FWhilst on the units, Georgia felt that
OL,16,Fstaff were not equipped to deal with
OL,17,Fthose struggling with eating
OL,18,Fdisorders. This meant behaviours
OL,19,Fconnected to her eating disorder often
OL,20,Fflew "under the radar" and she
OL,21,Fcontinued to lose weight.
