OL,7,FShe said: "I couldn't grasp why nobody
OL,8,Funderstood that this was really
OL,9,Fdifficult for me and putting a meal in
OL,10,Ffront of me isn't going to work.
OL,12,F"They need to have more training with
OL,13,Feating disorders. Because there was no
OL,14,Fbed for me anywhere else, it was like
OL,15,FI was just there, and nobody knew what
OL,16,Fto do with me. So they kind of just
OL,17,Fwatched me get worse.
