OL,7,F"That was really difficult for my
OL,8,Ffamily, because they were relieved
OL,9,Fthat I had finally received a bed in a
OL,10,Fhospital, which I really needed, but I
OL,11,Fcontinued to get worse."
OL,13,FGeorgia added how the use of agency
OL,14,Fstaff meant there were inconsistencies
OL,15,Fin her care, which she claims led to
OL,16,Fmistakes being made. She recounted how
OL,17,Fshe was able to hide food from the
OL,18,Fstaff who were not familiar with her
OL,19,Ftreatment plan.
