OL,7,F"I really needed that help, I was
OL,8,Fdesperate. I was hopeful for my life
OL,9,Fto begin again. It did eventually, but
OL,10,Fit took so much longer than it needed
OL,11,Fto.
OL,13,F"All of that time wasted where I had
OL,14,Fbeen deteriorating with limited
OL,15,Fsupport could have been prevented if I
OL,16,Fhad a smoother transition from CAMHS
OL,17,Fto adult services.
OL,19,F"It made the recovery period longer
OL,20,Fand so much more painful."
