OL,11,Fquality, safe and effective care.
OL,13,FIt also highlighted a recent Health
OL,14,FInspectorate Wales review of inpatient
OL,15,Fmental health services at Royal
OL,16,FGlamorgan Hospital, which acknowledged
OL,17,Fsignificant improvements.
