OL,7,FMind Cymru has urged the Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment to "take the lead" in
OL,9,Fimproving care for mental health
OL,10,Finpatients. It wants to see a focus on
OL,11,Ftackling staff shortages, care
OL,12,Fplanning and the use of restraints at
OL,13,Fmental health inpatient units across
OL,14,FWales.
