OL,7,FSue O'Leary, Director of Mind Cymru,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The Welsh Government has the
OL,9,Fchance to take the lead in caring for
OL,10,Fand protecting people who need
OL,11,Finpatient mental health support. This
OL,12,Freport is centred around the voices of
OL,13,Fpeople who have experienced first-hand
OL,14,Fthe ways in which inpatient care can
OL,15,Fhelp, but can also be dangerously
OL,16,Finadequate and lacking in dignity and
OL,17,Frespect.
OL,19,F"The rising tide of mental health need
OL,20,Fin Wales is significant, but we need
OL,21,Fmore
